syncfix3-fix6: DB hash mismatch tolerance

After 3 consecutive DB hash mismatches, force recalculate hash and proceed
with consensus. Uses db_hash_mismatch_count field in session struct.
Resets count to 0 on successful match or after forced recalc.

Applied to:
- dap_chain_cs_esbocs.c: replaced hard reject+break with progressive tolerance
- dap_chain_cs_esbocs.h: db_hash_mismatch_count field (already present)
